collectionMetadata.name: Relationship of Parties in Cases Registered at the Community Mediation Centre
collectionMetadata.description: Show the type of relationship between parties in cases registered at the Community Mediation Centre. These cases will be broken down into the following categories: Neighbour, Family, Friends, Commercial Entities, Commercial Entity and Individual, Colleagues, Landlord-Tenant, Strangers, Others. Prior to Dec 2014, the "Others" category included cases that are currently represented as "Landlord-Tenant" and "Strangers". After 2014, others include Former Lovers, Lovers, Former Colleagues, Tenant-Tenant.
